cialty programming videoondemand services consisting of access to movies national broadcast and cable network shows music videos and locally produced even mediacom broadband llc through its subsidiaries operates as a cable company in the united states it offers video highspeed data hsd and phone services to residential and small to mediumsized business customers over its hybrid fiber and coaxial cable network the company’s video services include the programming of local broadcast stations as well as public government and leased access channels national cable and regional sports networks foreignlanguage and international programming digital music channels and other specialty programming videoondemand services consisting of access to movies national broadcast and cable network shows music videos and locally produced events as well as special event programs and digital video recorder services that allow customers to record programming to view at their convenience it offers highspeed internet access to its hsd customers the company’s phone services include calling and other features such as caller id call waiting call forwarding and threeway calling it also provides fiberbased network and transport services to medium and largesized businesses governments and educational institutions sells advertising to local regional and national advertisers on television and digital platforms under the onmedia brand name and offers home security and automation services to residential customers as of december   mediacom broadband llc served approximately  video  hsd and  phone customers the company was founded in  and is based in new york new york mediacom broadband llc is a subsidiary of mediacom communications corporation detailed description  mediacom waymediacom parknew york ny united statesfounded in  employees phone  wwwmediacomcccom key executives for mediacom broadband llc mr rocco b commisso chief executive officer age  mr mark e stephan chief financial officer and executive v